@startuml
actor Buyer
actor Approver
participant "PR API" as API
participant "PurchaseRequest\nDomain" as Domain

Buyer -> API : Create PR
API -> Domain : new PurchaseRequest()
Domain --> API : PR (Draft)

Buyer -> API : Submit PR
API -> Domain : Submit()
Domain --> API : Status = Submitted

Approver -> API : Approve PR
API -> Domain : Approve()
Domain --> API : Status = Approved
@enduml